item.title: CVE-2022-1603|2024-08-03T00:10:03.703Z -- unknown -- mail%20subscribe%20list
item.description: The Mail Subscribe List WordPress plugin before 2.1.4 does not have CSRF check in place when deleting subscribed users, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin perform such action and delete arbitrary users from the subscribed list
